  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV6">
<l>taṭāviya vampum murinta cilaikaḷum pōkaviṭṭuk</l>
<l>kaṭāyiṉa koṇṭolkum valliyī tēṉu macurarmaṅkak</l>
<l>kaṭāviya vēkap paṟavaiyiṉ pākaṉ mataṉaceṅkō</l>
<l>ṉaṭāviya kūṟṟaṅkaṇ ṭīruyir kāmiṉkaḷ ñālattuḷḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This is the creeper who pines, setting free to go curved arrows and</l>
<l>broken bows, taking those that are serviceable. Even if [so], look at</l>
<l>Death who wields Madana’s just sceptre, from the driver of the swift bird</l> 
<l>urged so that the Asuras be diminuished, guard [your] lives in the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
